Path: godot/tutorials/inputs/custom_mouse_cursor.rst
Summary: Overview of available mouse cursor shapes and their usage considerations in Godot.

Cursor list
There are multiple mouse cursors you can define, documented in the Input.CursorShape enum. Which ones you want to use depends on your use case.